; ITERATIVE FIBONACCI, SHOWING ASSIGNMENT AND A `&` LOOP.
; ASSIGNMENT IS POSTFIX TOO: `VALUE NAME!` STORES VALUE INTO NAME.

!FIB N
    0 A!
    1 B!
    0 I!
    I N < &
        A B + T!
        B A!
        T B!
        I 1 + I!
    A @

!MAIN
    0 I!
    I 10 < &
        I FIB PRINT
        I 1 + I!
